This section contains automatically generated API documentation for Egregora.

All documentation is extracted from docstrings in the source code using [mkdocstrings](https://mkdocstrings.github.io/).

## Package Structure

- **Core**: Database schemas and core data structures
- **Ingestion**: WhatsApp export parsing
- **Privacy**: Anonymization and PII detection
- **Augmentation**: Content enrichment pipeline
- **Generation**: Blog post writing and editing agents
- **Knowledge**: RAG retrieval and ranking systems
- **Publication**: MkDocs site scaffolding
- **Orchestration**: CLI and pipeline orchestration
- **Utils**: Shared utilities and helpers

